{"tid":56552,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做Deloitte/ EY所謂4大到底係點？","createTime":"2016-12-27T10:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T11:06:08.000Z","uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bff6631e0a0f440ce7d66b1362d88318a6f8de9","tid":56552,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"利申先，soc sci final year搵緊工，對入big 4無興趣，只係出於好奇<br />\n<br />\n無乜研究呢個行業嘅野，對於呢d野好無知，由細到大聽翻來big 4都係好勁好難入嘅公司，但而家開始搵工後發現其實好多身邊人都入左，所以好好奇其實所謂big 4係咪真係咁難入？<br />\n<br />\n識好多商科人都做過big 4 intern，好多都係0經驗就被請左，識有一個，份人唔smart，英文唔好，非3大，做完deloitte都直接有graduate offer，ey都識一個，第一份intern就係ey，被請時resume完全空白，聽人講kpmg都沒落緊。<br />\n<br />\n有另外一個朋友係澳洲deloitte做，做完一個月intern已經上左岸，有個邊嘅return offer，話起薪點有3萬。<br />\n<br />\n咁其實big 4到底係點？人工幾多？難唔難入？recruitment過程係點？前景？<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位巴絲解答下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd771d8a4c33354b6ef8d9cdb615138cb2666ca","tid":56552,"uid":2153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"13000左右<br />\n<br />\n你講得岩，大部份team都易入。吹大左"},{"pid":"1be1c7bf1af458b44f84967d713354ea60e87dd2","tid":56552,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>13000左右<br />\n<br />\n你講得岩，大部份team都易入。吹大左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都聽講過係起薪13k<br />\n<br />\n有話之後會升得好快，但好似好多人熬唔到就走左？"},{"pid":"88947483c8060f28135e0022838c032da5dbd999","tid":56552,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"入big four post睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd70b9c290d7933cc076e9b54982942715de8e8b","tid":56552,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}